article_title: A Victory For Medicare Part D

article_metadata.author: Doug Schoen

og.description: The start to this week brought with it an important new development for our failing healthcare system. This development augurs well for Medicare Part D and will hopefully keep it working effectively for Medicare patients at a time when questions continue to be asked about the Affordable Care Act, its implementation [...]
